Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.07,0:00:06.09,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这里是航天短讯200418期
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.43,0:00:11.83,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据航天爱好者网消息 航天科工火箭技术有限公司
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:16.68,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}负责行云01 02星发射的快舟一号甲遥6火箭的试验队员
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.87,0:00:20.59,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}正在酒泉卫星发射中心附近的火车上进行隔离
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.90,0:00:22.07,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据小道消息
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.12,0:00:28.11,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}此次进场的不只是这枚快舟1号甲 还有原定于年初发射的快舟11号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.36,0:00:31.60,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快舟11号个头更大 直径2.2米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.73,0:00:32.96,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}质量78吨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.16,0:00:34.96,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}近地轨道运力1.5吨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.20,0:00:37.53,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}700km太阳同步轨道运力1吨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.37,0:00:40.92,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}相比于长征11号的直径2米
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:42.64,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}质量57.6吨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:44.72,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}近地轨道运力700kg
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:48.53,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}700km太阳同步轨道运力350至400kg
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.85,0:00:50.72,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快舟11号都要更强一些
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.27,0:00:51.99,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据了解
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.20,0:00:55.53,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}快舟11号采用的碳纤维复合材料作为壳体
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:58.47,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}也许是因为这项技术提升了很多性能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.19,0:01:02.96,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}另外根据快舟火箭首席科学家助理的微博评论区
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.00,0:01:05.02,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}由于之前的种种影响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:09.49,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}目前快舟1号甲遥六火箭发射延期 具体时间未定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.75,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可能会在5月份
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.23,0:01:15.23,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据俄罗斯航天集团总裁罗戈津的推特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:18.70,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}俄罗斯科学号实验舱开始真空测试
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:20.23,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}持续差不多一个月
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.52,0:01:22.71,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之后会开始准备运往拜科努尔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.09,0:01:24.76,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}根据之前罗戈津的说法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.00,0:01:27.94,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}科学号实验舱将于2021年初发射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.12,0:01:30.21,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而不是原定的2020年底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.81,0:01:33.34,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}科学号实验舱始建于90年代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.70,0:01:37.40,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}最初是按照曙光号功能货舱的备份进行制造的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:38.89,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}中间历经波折
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:41.28,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其总质量20.257吨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:43.04,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}长13.1米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.39,0:01:45.88,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}太阳能帆板展开长度23.9米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.98,0:01:49.25,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据NASA局长布里登斯廷的推特
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:53.58,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}NASA将载人龙Demo-2任务定于5月27日进行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.11,0:01:59.34,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}载人龙Demo-2将使用全新的B1058猎鹰9号火箭进行发射
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:01.60,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}宇航员道格拉斯赫尔利
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.86,0:02:03.55,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}和宇航员罗伯特本肯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.63,0:02:04.67,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}将进行搭乘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.06,0:02:07.91,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这两位宇航员都是参与过航天飞机任务的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.60,0:02:14.96,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其中道格拉斯赫尔利还是最后一次航天飞机任务STS-135的驾驶员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:17.44,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}某种程度上可以看得出
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.58,0:02:20.78,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}NASA非常重视此次龙2飞船载人首飞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.59,0:02:23.17,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}据SpaceNews消息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.50,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}诺斯罗普格鲁曼公司宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.73,0:02:29.78,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Intelsat-901在2月25日与MEV-1对接后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.28,0:02:33.76,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}于4月2日重新进入地球同步轨道并恢复运营
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.27,0:02:35.07,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}MEV-1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.60,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}全称Mission Extension Vehicle-1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.00,0:02:39.39,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}任务拓展卫星-1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:41.55,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}现在由诺格公司运营
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.99,0:02:46.07,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}于2019年10月9日通过质子M火箭发射入轨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.56,0:02:48.16,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}其携带特殊的装置
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:52.49,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}可以一般的通信卫星的发动机燃烧室进行对接并固定
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.88,0:02:54.39,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通过电推的方式
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.44,0:02:58.91,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}帮助Intelsat-901保持5年的轨道至2025年2月28日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:03.01,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}随后 它会对另外两枚卫星进行类似的操作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:04.97,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}并分别延续5年寿命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.69,0:03:08.65,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}由于保轨时卫星必须和服务对象连接
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.94,0:03:10.26,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}导致效率较低
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:13.49,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}诺格将不会批量生产类似MEV-1的卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.49,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而是只生产到MEV-2
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.02,0:03:16.60,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.74,0:03:18.04,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通过研制MRV
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.21,0:03:19.92,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}Mission Robotic Vehicle
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:20.82,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来替代MEV
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.46,0:03:23.86,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}MRV可以释放多个任务扩展舱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.25,0:03:25.62,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}通过任务扩展舱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.10,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}来让MRV一次服务多个卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:32.54,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}使得MRV在服务过程中不需要一直对接目标卫星
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.62,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}而是通过扩展舱来对接
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:37.02,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}这样可以提高服务效率
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.72,0:03:40.17,1080P-src-hans-sans-medi-75,,0,0,0,,{\blur4}接下来是未来一周的发射预报
